data.description: Run Don't walk !!! This is the best price in the community for this style house. New carpet, fresh earth tone paint. Plenty of windows in the 2 story family brightens up the house with fresh sunlight.  Quiet Cul-de-sac, wooded big back yard, leveled lot. The master bedroom has a spacious sitting area which could be used as a study or office. Top schools, swim and tennis community. Surrounded by plenty of shopping and top restaurants. New laminate waterproof flooring covers the entire downstairs.  Big open floor plan, surrounded by some of the best parks gwinnett county has to offer. New trendsetting ceiling fans in all the bedrooms,  Run Don't walk,  this is the best, the biggest, the most affordable New house in gwinnett county for this price point. The house feels New, looks new, but doesn't have that new house price tag. The award winning paint color throughout the house is agreeable grey. These types of deals don't come around every day.
